{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-30-2",
 "title": "Whiskey and Swoop Talk in Mos Eisley",
 "summary": "Setting the Triton down in Mos Eisley, the disguised NRI agent Bazil McKenzie (as Mege Vauki) once again runs into the Griffon hauler Khirsah, marking their third chance meeting in a week. Bazil claims to be visiting his mother and old friends on his homeworld, and the two agree to talk swoops over a drink. In Chalmun's Cantina, joined by the Twi'lek Xanatos, Bazil dispenses swoop-racing advice -- recommending the Oblivion Skyrazer and pricey upgrades -- while sharing a rare bottle of pre-Endor Corellian whiskey. The pair bond at length over their shared connoisseurship of fine and fading liquors, trading tales of vintages and lamenting how popularity ruins good drinks, before Khirsah takes a glass to go and departs with his usual half-wave, both certain fate will throw them together again.",
